enhanced_by.reason: Both methods involve selecting elements based on evaluators, which can be reused for setting up the test environment.
The addElement method can be used to add elements to the form, which can be useful for setting up the test environment for elements method.

The select method with a CSS query can be used to verify the elements selected by the elements method, providing a way to construct assertions.
